trends: There has been one other sighting in Chengdu
There were no other sightings in Chengdu on or around August 21st 2009
divs: Sighting DetailsThat nights in Chengdu, Sichuan region found that UFO, the object body of the light source can be clearer to see, it has a white light and red light and it has the size of a small car, suspended in the air and can move around. I was away from the level of those objects from 700-800 m, the object from the ground about six storeys high. I did not hear any sound. August 21, 2009
